{"tid":224875,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[自製][更新] Overwatch全新即時組隊系統 根據MAIN黎組隊 再冇TROLL隊友 #2","createTime":"2017-05-01T11:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T09:53:18.000Z","uid":112612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"220a0ace6acdc8acaf54e45664e5906775251cdb","tid":224875,"uid":112612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:28:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[更新]</span></strong></span><br />\n前幾日更新關左個server 多謝上次有支持既巴打 依家開返同埋今次加左d野：<br />\n1. Public chat room 比所有玩家都可以交流<br />\n2. 依家係team入面既chat room會留50條messages records <br />\n<br />\n希望呢次更新方便大家知道其他人係唔係度 同埋溝通得更加好 <br />\n另外開左instagram: overcrews 有咩更新都會係instagram講 當然連登都會提多次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[系統簡介]</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n網址：<a href=\"https://www.overcrews.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.overcrews.com%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=35f8dc39\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.overcrews.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://呢個系統係用battle.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%91%A2%E5%80%8B%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E4%BF%82%E7%94%A8battle.net&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=dd592462\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">呢個系統係用battle.net</a>黎認證玩家身份 再比玩家揀佢地既ROLE（e.g. Support)<br />\n然後根據佢地既ROLE黎分隊 希望解決同隊撞哂MAIN搞到有人TROLL既問題 （例如4隊support main一隊）<br />\n<br />\n大家可以試下用 有咩問題可以係度反映同問 或者EMAIL去overcrews@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n基本流程：<br />\n1. 登入 Battle Net <br />\n2. 揀你平時玩開(/想玩)既Role (e.g. Support) 之後可以係Profile度轉<br />\n3. 揀你平時玩開既Server 之後可以係Profile度轉<br />\n4. 之後就註冊完成 你可以開TEAM或者入人地TEAM<br />\n4a. 開team：打個TEAM既名 之後揀你想你果隊有咩ROLE既人 TOTAL要揀5個<br />\n諗唔到可以揀ANY 如果你唔洗搵哂5個人既 可以關左其中一D位置佢<br />\n4b. 入人地team：你會見到你符合要求既TEAM 揀返岩既ROLE就可以加入<br />\n5. 入左team又confirm好哂就加係game度加大家既battle tag 然後就開波啦<br />\n<br />\n特色：<br />\n1. 根據你既RANK黎分配隊伍 你唔會見到同你個RANK差太遠既人<br />\n2. 根據你既ROLE黎分配隊伍 解決同隊撞MAIN ROLE既問題<br />\n3. 每個玩家既TOP 3 HERO會顯示出黎 可以用黎做組隊時既參考<br />\n4. 隊伍房間入面有CHAT ROOM方便玩家溝通"},{"pid":"db1c9c972aeef70ed3a6d616647cc02bee75ef29","tid":224875,"uid":112612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:31:07.000Z","msg":"上一個post既link：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/220826/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/220826/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"da6983701cd84253d50de18350e4ddef581d6173","tid":224875,"uid":112612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:57:20.000Z","msg":"pushhhh"},{"pid":"7ef0206462f2805bda2bd10cf2ebbd347594c1a0","tid":224875,"uid":7475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:11:33.000Z","msg":"即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6efa3bff357d43eb4188fdadf3f1e159da4af67","tid":224875,"uid":736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:42:39.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"82cde3e53c8ed7ed4a30dea80ce2e0f533137eb7","tid":224875,"uid":112612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:09:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係禁入去試下就知"},{"pid":"d0f33eaacb69d7e2baf8df042a62c1057e9434db","tid":224875,"uid":736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T19:36:14.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"fb47e7c8acbb0d789173aea792ff2c83e106cf3d","tid":224875,"uid":65237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T02:29:02.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80fb2ee6841bde951f94fbedd398591d200da3ac","tid":224875,"uid":112612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T09:02:11.000Z","msg":"已經有巴打成功組左隊啦 大家都快d試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開左個group放係度等下人就會有"},{"pid":"6fbbb3c6827d27e02e18e17dd9ed9ebb37e89be9","tid":224875,"ui